headline: Gartner Survey Finds 73% of CSOs Are Prioritizing Growth from Existing Customers for 2025
summary: LAS VEGAS, May 20, 2025--Seventy-three percent of CSOs are prioritizing growth from existing customers for 2025, according to a survey by Gartner, Inc.
